data.description: Located in Oakdale. This 3bed 2 bath home is sitting in a cul-de-sac in a quiet neighborhood. Close to the park. Front has beautiful mature trees and flower beds that bloom full in spring. Huge back yard has working pond with fish.  Ready for a new family or investor adding to their portfolio.
